Email::Filter::SpamAssassin version 0.0.1

This module is a subclass of Email::Filter which integrates
Mail::SpamAssassin. It has only one additional method.


INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install


DEPENDENCIES

Email::Filter, Mail::SpamAssassin


